                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "L’ITALIE ? Elle est dans le train\nExtraordinaire qui s’emporte\nMême au-delà des flots du Rhin,\nMême en-deçà de notre Porte !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "L’Autriche, elle est bien bonne là,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Non sans son « laurier » sur son shak'",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "O, la Prusse qu’on consola*",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Par telles cessions dont chaque",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "L’Autriche, elle est bien bonne là,\nNon sans son « laurier » sur son shak'\nO, la Prusse qu’on consola*\nPar telles cessions dont chaque"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Est si terrible qu’il ne faut",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Aucunement espérer trêve",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Ni paix sans reprendre de haut !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Strasbourg et Metz, hélas ! et Trêve !…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Est si terrible qu’il ne faut\nAucunement espérer trêve\nNi paix sans reprendre de haut !\nStrasbourg et Metz, hélas ! et Trêve !…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Et quant à ce… gouvernement",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Qui prétend garder l’équilibre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "En l’occurrence, ou bien il ment",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Ou bien la France n’est pas libre !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et quant à ce… gouvernement\nQui prétend garder l’équilibre\nEn l’occurrence, ou bien il ment\nOu bien la France n’est pas libre !"
        }
    ],
